I lost my three best friends that became family, their cousin put in a coma, lost my regular life, with guilt crossing my mind daily. Every day I try to put a smile on my face for those around me, people giving me hate for the situation I’m in hurts but I know god made me a survivor for a reason. Oh ira you’re music has helped me in ways I cannot explain. I broke both legs, a rib, my ancle, and my nose. I was in a coma for 30+ hours and it’s a miracle I’m alive. Thank you for your music and your genuine soul.
